<threat_model>
## Trust Boundaries

| Boundary | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| build-tooling ??? committed tree | The scratch harness must NEVER mutate committed 
swg.sln/.vcxproj (D-01); accidental commit of x64 platform entries would pre-empt Phase 33 and 
corrupt the 32-bit build contract |
| compile-flag parity ??? BITS-03 size asserts | Missing `_USE_32BIT_TIME_T=1` in the harness 
silently widens `time_t` to 8 bytes on x64, making later BITS-03 size asserts baseline to the wrong 
value |

## STRIDE Threat Register

| Threat ID | Category | Component | Disposition | Mitigation Plan |
|-----------|----------|-----------|-------------|-----------------|
| T-31-01 | Tampering | committed swg.sln / .vcxproj | mitigate | Task 3 acceptance asserts `grep -c 
x64 swg.sln == 0` and scratch dir untracked; .gitignore line (Task 1) makes accidental staging 
impossible |
| T-31-02 | Tampering | time_t serialization width | mitigate | props carries `_USE_32BIT_TIME_T=1` 
(Task 2 acceptance greps for it); preserves 32-bit `time_t` so later size asserts are baselined 
correctly |
| T-31-03 | Info disclosure | none (local build tooling, no network/PII) | accept | Compile-only 
harness produces only local .obj + a log; no external surface |
</threat_model>

